x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F68xQn4kUd5-Oi8UXwNeVBoBGIP9DdafcwjVawsI1WsI_Jd8kl_1200x0.jpg&h=4a107bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNBA 球隊候斯頓火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）日前於 Twitter 上載圖片支持香港示威者，其後引起大批中國籃球迷不滿，群起抵制，最後被迫刪帖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人同我上佢twitter留言撐佢</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係連鍵戰都輸比中国人呀嘛?</span></span><br />\n<strong>Daryl Morel twitter: </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/dmorey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdmorey&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=ff5c5713\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dmorey</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要比任何撐香港既人知道, 大部份群眾都係撐佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無理由令佢地比班<span style=\"color: pink;\">愛国粉紅</span>洗板而<span style=\"color: red;\">滅聲</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fdc4c13fb7f4038d22d86ab83a0d105c9a055ebf","tid":1629474,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcee36fe51345c03656843eacfc1a818d1876a69","tid":1629474,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a231ba331386693d3b7fdad125b2ed16835c3b26","tid":1629474,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n